# 6. Debugging History & Failure Modes

**Freshness: ✅ High.**

- **Stale Alembic temp table:** an interrupted SQLite batch migration left
  `_alembic_tmp_test_cases`; rerun failed. Resolution: remove controlled stale artifacts and inspect
  live columns to resume safely.
- **Populated foreign-key rebuild:** batch-altering `test_cases` attempted to drop a referenced
  parent and failed. Resolution: native additive `ADD COLUMN` operations plus populated-FK test.
- **Cold direct Streamlit route:** direct `/evaluate` before page registration showed overlay/error.
  Resolution for current scope: root-first supported entry and E2E path; true deep-link fix remains P3.
- **Container smoke 422:** temporary proof script filtered provider name `deterministic`, while demo
  profiles use provider `demo` and API mode `deterministic`. Corrected proof selection to API mode;
  product behavior was unaffected.
- **Host port collision:** unrelated
  `/Users/fortunevieyra/Documents/Github/ai-projects/codebase-intelligence` owned port 8000 during
  final container proof. It was not stopped; final checks used `dashboard -> api:8000`.
- **Misleading metadata:** real-adapter registry omitted the built-in deterministic adapter.
  Resolution: metadata prepends `deterministic`; test and final-image readback added.
- **Noisy success traps avoided:** local browser proof was not called production proof; Docker health
  was not flattened into hosted proof; mocked providers were not called live proof.

